{"tid":1506802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台上撻落地　Jackson＠GOT7開騷出意外","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T02:30:06.000Z","uid":1121,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2e55d82d287d9b7019ab608076cf007eb93b84dd","tid":1506802,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190826/photo/bkn-20190826054852519-0826_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190826063047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190826054852519-0826_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190826063047&h=234ffdd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舞台意外時時有，唔少藝人因為咁受傷，呢日韓國男團GOT7喺墨爾本開巡唱，當中香港成員王嘉爾（Jackson）喺表演途中，想行落台同粉絲近距離接觸時，喺台邊差錯腳撻咗落地，佢即時痛到唔郁得瞓咗喺地，一班粉絲嚇到個心離一離，好彩隔咗一陣佢開始有反應，跟住揮手向粉絲示意冇事，起返身繼續落力獻唱盡顯專業，見佢表現如，一班粉絲個心先至番！"},{"pid":"a5587bb224e150fdfb348f119e04c7035f843c77","tid":1506802,"uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"China man<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86469a9c0a3ee6b5056a60615e4b7c46888f1d4c","tid":1506802,"uid":62569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:19:35.000Z","msg":"天有眼，半身不遂未"},{"pid":"f0772982560244230e66657a2226cd5f2352547a","tid":1506802,"uid":76632,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"我幫他護旗<br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịlḷịị\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Bl%E1%B8%B7%E1%BB%8B%E1%BB%8B&h=6e6c36a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0a46b12262c640aefd6cbb9498eedb76751bb37","tid":1506802,"uid":85457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:24:29.000Z","msg":"支那人"},{"pid":"e03fc9aa50d5b3e7e8e4c1a57ff1d46ad15741f6","tid":1506802,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:25:13.